body.description: The Gillette ProGlide men's razor with FlexBall technology responds to your contours giving you uncompromising closeness and comfort. The handle’s FlexBall technology responds to contours and the blade refill features 5 antifriction blades for a shave you can barely feel. The blades are spaced closely together for incredible comfort with a precision trimmer on the back for hard to reach places and for styling your facial hair just the way you want it. The enhanced lubrastrip (vs. Fusion5) has more lubricants for comfort and glide. This enhanced lubrastrip also fades when you are no longer getting an optimal shave. Soft microfins gently stretch and smooth your skin to prepare hairs for a close shave while a microcomb helps guide your hair for a close shave from our thinnest blades. The ProGlide razor for men features our sharpest blades (first 4 blades) which help get virtually every hair effortlessly. One razor blade refill lasts up to one month of shaves. All ProGlide blade refills can fit all Gillette 5 blade razor handles (excluding GilletteLabs).

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Title: A Close Shave to Perfection - Gillette ProGlide Razors Review
reviews.reviewText: I recently had the pleasure of trying out the Gillette ProGlide Razors, and I must say, they exceeded all my expectations! As someone who takes grooming seriously, I'm always on the lookout for a razor that not only provides a smooth shave but also offers a comfortable and hassle-free experience. The ProGlide Razors checked all the boxes and more.First and foremost, the quality of the blades is outstanding. They effortlessly glide over my skin, delivering an incredibly close shave with minimal effort. Even on those days when I have some stubborn stubble, the ProGlide Razors tackle the task with ease, leaving my skin feeling remarkably smooth and irritation-free. The precision trimmer is an added bonus, allowing me to shape my facial hair with precision and style.One of the standout features of the ProGlide Razors is their FlexBall technology. The razor's head pivots effortlessly, easily adapting to the contours of my face, neck, and jawline. This design innovation ensures that no area is left untouched, resulting in a consistently even shave every time.Beyond the impeccable performance, I was pleasantly surprised by the razor's durability. The blades seem to maintain their sharpness for a significantly longer time compared to other razors I've used in the past. This means fewer blade changes and more value for my money, which is always appreciated.As for the comfort factor, the ProGlide Razors truly excel. The lubrication strips with enhanced glide make each stroke feel smooth and soothing, reducing any potential irritation or razor burns. I can confidently say that my shaving experience has become a delight since I started using these razors.Furthermore, the ergonomic handle design offers a comfortable grip, ensuring a steady hand and an overall satisfying shaving experience. It's evident that Gillette has put a lot of thought into the design, making the ProGlide Razors a pleasure to use.Lastly, let's talk about the price point. Considering the outstanding performance, comfort, and durability, the Gillette ProGlide Razors are reasonably priced. It's an investment in a top-notch shaving tool that I won't hesitate to make again and again.In conclusion, I highly recommend the Gillette ProGlide Razors to anyone seeking a premium shaving experience. Whether you have sensitive skin, a thick beard, or simply want a reliable razor, this product delivers on all fronts. Prepare to be impressed by the smoothness, precision, and overall satisfaction you'll get from the ProGlide Razors. Trust me; your grooming routine will never be the same again!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Unbeatable Performance and Precision: Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors Review
reviews.reviewText: Introduction:The quest for the perfect shave ends with Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors. Packed with cutting-edge technology and superior craftsmanship, this remarkable grooming tool offers an unparalleled shaving experience. In this review, we delve into the key features, performance, and overall value of the Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors, along with the convenience of the accompanying blade refills.Cutting-edge Technology for a Flawless Shave:The Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razor boasts an impressive array of technological advancements that elevate the shaving experience. Equipped with thin, fine blades, this razor effortlessly glides across the skin, ensuring an incredibly close and comfortable shave. The innovative FlexBall technology allows the razor to pivot and adapt to the contours of your face, effortlessly reaching every nook and cranny for a precise and thorough shave.Unrivaled Performance:When it comes to performance, the Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors truly shine. The blades are expertly engineered to reduce tug and pull, making each stroke feel smooth and effortless. The result? A shave that is both gentle on the skin and incredibly effective at removing even the most stubborn facial hair. Whether you have coarse stubble or sensitive skin, this razor delivers a clean and irritation-free shave every time.Superior Comfort and Ergonomics:The Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razor not only excels in performance but also prioritizes user comfort. The handle is thoughtfully designed with an ergonomic grip, ensuring maximum control and maneuverability while shaving. The razor's weight is perfectly balanced, providing a comfortable and stable shaving experience, even during prolonged use. Say goodbye to hand fatigue and hello to a comfortable and enjoyable grooming routine.Long-lasting and Convenient Blade Refills:The package includes four razor blade refills, ensuring you can maintain your shaving routine without interruption. Each blade refill is precision-engineered to deliver the same exceptional performance as the original razor. The convenience of the refill system means you won't have to worry about running out of blades, saving you time and effort in purchasing replacements.Conclusion:In summary, the Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors with its exceptional technology, outstanding performance, and user-friendly design is a game-changer in the world of shaving. Its ability to provide a close and comfortable shave, along with the convenience of the blade refill system, makes it a standout choice for men seeking a superior grooming experience. Say goodbye to razor burns and say hello to flawlessly smooth skin with the Gillette Fusion ProGlide Razors.
